name: 주인공
dialog: Oh, it's you! It's been a while.

name: Nari
dialog: I came to play you a song I made today.

name: Nari
dialog: The song title is “Smile Song.” Listen carefully

name: 주인공
dialog: Wow~ I made it really well and it's so exciting!

name: 주인공
dialog: Listening to the song makes me smile, hahaha.

name: 주인공
dialog: How did you make this song?

name: Nari
dialog: I made it because I thought it would be good to listen to when I'm feeling down or upset.

name: Nari
dialog: Listening to good music makes you feel good and relaxed, right?

name: Nari
dialog: The power of music is really amazing, isn't it?

name: 주인공
dialog: Right. I also like to sing!

name: Nari
dialog: Yes! Then, would you sing the song I made often?

name: 주인공
dialog: Sure. Nari, thank you for playing me such a nice song!
